    <section id="contextual_menu_actions_in_the_attributes_view">
      <title>Contextual Menu Actions in the Attributes View</title>
      <p id="p_wzv_bgk_54b">The following actions are available in the contextual menu of the
          <uicontrol>Attributes</uicontrol> view when editing in <uicontrol>Text</uicontrol>
        mode:</p>
      <p id="p_xzv_bgk_54b">
        <dl id="dl_yzv_bgk_54b">
          <dlentry id="dlentry_zzv_bgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol>Add</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Allows you to insert a new attribute. <ph
                product="author editor authorEclipse editorEclipse">Adding an attribute that is not
                in the list of all defined attributes is not possible when the <xref
                  keyref="options_editor_edit-modes_author_schema-aware">Allow only insertion of
                  valid elements and attributes</xref> schema-aware option is selected.</ph></dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-editing-modes/set-empty-value-dlentry" id="dlentry_a1w_bgk_54b">
            <dt/>
            <dd/>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-editing-modes/remove-dlentry" id="dlentry_b1w_bgk_54b">
            <dt/>
            <dd/>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-editing-modes/copy_dlentry" id="dlentry_c1w_bgk_54b">
            <dt/>
            <dd/>
